      <title>天空新闻称 Blackstone 准备进行新的 Hipgnosis 投标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/blackstone-prepares-to-make-fresh-hipgnosis-bid-sky-news-says</link>
